<div class="video-container">
	<%= video_tag("shibuya.mov", :style=>"width:100%;", :autoplay => true, :loop => true, :muted=> true ) %>
	<div class="video-headline">
		<h1>Share your bucket list<br>Tricket</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="video-credit">
		<p>©︎iStock.com/Sushiman</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid">
	<div class="row" style="height:300px; background-color:#EFE9D1;">
		<div class="col-md-12">
			<div class="home-headline title_type1">
				<h1>About Us</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="home-content">
				<h4>This website, <strong>"Tricket Japan"</strong> is for both<br>
				<strong>travelers from overseas</strong> who wanna share and accomplish your bucket list of exploring Japan<br>
			    <strong> & locals in Japan</strong> who would love to spread charm of Japan and improve your language skill.</h4>
			    <h2>皆さんの語学力を活かして日本を旅する外国人を手助けしませんか？</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row" style="height:300px;">
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<div class="home-headline title_type1_traveler">
				<h1>Travelers</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="home-content">
				<h4>Welcome to "Tricket Japan"!! Please share your bucket list with Japanese friends.
					They will definitely help you to make your dream come true.</h4>
				<p>ex. You may wanna see Japanese Monkey in Onsen(Japanese hotspring) or look for any delicious Japanese Sushi restaurant.</p>
				<h4>Click below to start your journey!!</h4>
				<h1><%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path(type_user: 0), class:"label label-default", :style=>"background-color:#f8b500;" %></h1>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<div class="home-headline title_type1_local">
				<h1>Locals (日本在住の方)</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="home-content">
				<h4>Welcome to "Tricket Japan"!! Are you ready to help travelers from oversea and introduce Japanese culture? It gonna help you to improve your language skill as well. Click below to start your journey!!</h4>
				<h4>ようこそ "Tricket Japan" へ!! 旅する外国人を手助けする準備はできていますか？ 下のボタンから新規登録へ。</h4>
				<h1><%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path(type_user: 1), class:"label label-default", :style=>"background-color:#9e3d3f;" %></h1>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row" style="background-color:#EFE9D1;">
		<div class="home-headline title_type1"  style="margin-left:20px;">
			<h1>How to user Tricket / Tricketの楽しみ方</h1>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row" style="background-color:#EFE9D1;">
		<div class="col-md-8">
			<div class="home-content" style="text-indent: -2em; padding-left: 5em;">
				<h4>① ”新規登録の際に「Traveler(主に日本への旅行者)」または「Local(主に日本人の方)」をお選びいただきます。</h4>
				<h4>② Travelerは、日本で叶えたい夢や、ちょっとしたやりたいこと、困っていることなどを投稿できます。このサイトでは、
				その投稿をTricket (Trip + Bucket list) と呼びます。</h4>
				<h4>③ Localは、そのTricketに対してコメントやダイレクトメッセージでTravelerの夢のお手伝いやアドバイスをします。</h4>
				<h4>④人気のあるTricketやユーザのランキングを確認したり、お気に入り機能、通知機能を利用したりすることで、このサイトをより一層お楽しみいただけるはずです。また、Tricketを書き留めておきたい方は、非公開にすることでシェアをせずにマイページに保存しておくことができます。</h4>
				<h4>⑤このサイト"Tricket"によって、世界中の人が日本で叶えたい夢を共有し、日本人と外国人の繋がりが深くなることを祈っています。</h4>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-4">
			<div class="image-top1">
				<%= image_tag asset_path "spring_sakura.jpg" %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row" style="background-color:#EFE9D1;">
		<div class="col-md-4">
			<div class="image-top2">
				<%= image_tag asset_path "winter_pawdersnow.jpg" %>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-8">
			<div class="home-content" style="text-indent: -2em; padding-left: 5em;">
				<h4>① Your journey will start with a registration to this website. On the registration, you can choose “Traveler(mainly for travelers from overseas)” or “Local(mainly for Japanese).</h4>
				<h4>② Travelers post your bucket list, your dream, or even something you need help with. On this website, we name bucket list as "Tricket" (Trip + Bucket list). </h4>
				<h4>③ Locals help travelers with Trickets they post, and give them advices through comments or messages.</h4>
				<h4>④ With the functions this website provide, for example, favorite function and  notification function, your journey must be more enjoyable. And also, you can keep your Trickets to yourself if you wish not to share them.</h4>
				<h4>⑤ We hope people all over the world share their dreams and deepen engagement with each other.</h4>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>